data.name: Pharm-Rx Chemical Corp.
data.description: Pharm-Rx has built an exceptional reputation since 1991 as an importer and distributor of active ingredients to the pharmaceutical, nutritional supplement, and food industries. We are extremely selective with our suppliers and personally visit manufacturers overseas. Our sustained growth is attributed to three core values of quality ingredients, competitive pricing, and unsurpassed customer service.

data.name: Bio-Active
data.description: Bio-Active™ Shark Cartilage Powder, a product born from a patented process, offering a potent, natural solution for inflammation and tissue repair. With robust anti-angiogenic properties, it inhibits new blood vessel growth to combat tumors and diseases. Safeguard your bone, joint, and connective tissues with natural chondroitin sulfate, an exceptional anti-inflammatory agent. Boost your immunity, promote tissue repair, and maintain the health of your joints and limbs.

data.name: Hydro-MC
data.description: Hydro-MC™ marine hydrolyzed collagen offers dual moisturizing benefits for skin and hair. Enriched with polysaccharides, vitamins, and vital sea minerals, it fosters the healing and structural integrity of connective tissue. Collagen, the fundamental protein in ligaments, joints, hair, skin, and nails, bolsters our body's structural support. It supports connective tissue and joint functions, rebuilds synovial fluid, provides a rich source of protein and collagen, and can be seamlessly integrated into cosmetic creams and functional beverages.

data.name: SCP-Active
data.description: SCP-Active™ Shark Cartilage Powder is a dynamic solution, harnessing a blend of potent nutrients to combat joint inflammation, subsequently alleviating pain and enhancing mobility. Its exceptional content of chondroitin sulfate, glycosaminoglycans (GAGs), calcium, and phosphorus promotes the restoration of damaged joints and tendons. Experience reduced pain, stiffness, and inflammation, while enjoying improved joint mobility, thanks to its wealth of anti-inflammatory compounds. Moreover, it strengthens the immune system, boasts anti-angiogenic properties to limit blood vessel growth, and bolsters your body's ability to ward off disease.

data.name: ABA-active
data.description: ABA-Active™ a powerhouse of natural vitality. This nutrient-rich supplement enhances liver function and overall health, boosting stamina with essential minerals and vitamins. Packed with omega-3 and omega-9 fatty acids for heart health and improved circulation. Loaded with glycosaminoglycans (GAGs) and verified anti-inflammatory benefits by NZ Plant and Food Research. Plus, it's a source of energy, promoting sexual function and aiding in the reduction of harm caused by non-fresh, oxidized food and excessive alcohol.

data.name: Pharm-Rx Amla Extract
data.description: Pharm-Rx Amla Extract is derived from a natural plant origin, containing hydrolyzable tannin as its active component. This ingredient is naturally derived and plant-based.

data.name: Pharm-Rx Calcium Lysinate
data.description: Pharm-Rx Calcium Lysinate is a mineral source for pharma and nutraceuticals. The ingredient, calcium lysinate, is a type of calcium mineral.

data.name: Pharm-Rx Barium Sulfate
data.description: Pharm-Rx Barium Sulfate is a cosmetic ingredient that functions as an opacifier and pigment.

data.name: Pharm-Rx Apple Cider Vinegar Powder
data.description: Pharm-Rx Apple Cider Vinegar Powder is a dietary supplement in powder form. It is formulated to provide the benefits of apple cider vinegar in a convenient and versatile powdered format. This product falls under the category of nutraceuticals and supplements, specifically in the supplements and functional ingredients sector within the pharmaceuticals and nutraceuticals technologies.

featured_products.name: Nattokinase 20,000

featured_products.name: Afrigetics PelaPower™ (Pelargonium Sidoides Spray-Dried Extract)
featured_products.description: PelaPower™ is a sustainably sourced extract of Pelargonium sidoides that is used as an active ingredient in cold and flu products.

featured_products.name: Afrigetics Kannaease™ (Sceletium Tortuosum)
featured_products.description: KannaEase™ is a standardized extract of Sceletium tortuosum, derived from a traditional South African succulent, known for its mood-enhancing and stress-reducing properties.

featured_products.name: Nattiase® (Nattokinase)
featured_products.description: Nattiase®: A high-nattokinase fermented soybean extract for cardiovascular health. Enhances circulation, supports blood pressure, and improves lipid profiles.

featured_products.name: Bordas Diosmin (Citrus Sinensis)
featured_products.description: Diosmin, derived from Sweet Orange, offers cardioprotective and venotonic benefits. With 100+ years of expertise Bordas excels in natural product development and manufacturing

featured_products.name: Bordas Hesperidin (Citrus Sinensis)
featured_products.description: Hesperidin, derived from Sweet Oranges, promotes blood circulation and cardiovascular health. With 100+ years of expertise, Bordas excels in natural product development.

featured_products.name: Bordas Naringin (Citrus Paradisi)

These cacao butter chunks offer a high-quality organic option for various chocolate applications.

data.name: Ecoandino Organic Criollo Cacao Butter Coins
data.description: Ecoandino Organic Criollo Cacao Butter Coins are ideal for chocolate making, whether you're creating white chocolate, milk chocolate, or dark chocolate. With a creamy to light yellow color, these cacao butter coins bring a natural and appealing hue to your chocolate creations. Notably, the product is gluten-free, GMO-free, and additive-free, catering to dietary preferences and ensuring a pure cacao flavor.

data.name: Ecoandino Organic Gelatinized Maca Powder
data.description: Ecoandino Organic Gelatinized Maca Powder, with its light brown color, is a versatile and wholesome addition to various culinary creations. This gluten-free, GMO-free, additive-free, and non-irradiated product offers a natural and pure maca experience. Conveniently, it can be directly mixed into yogurts, smoothies, and dairy products, enhancing their nutritional profile. Moreover, it serves as a delightful ingredient in desserts, chocolate bars, cakes, and other baked goods, providing both flavor and nutritional benefits to your favorite treats.

data.name: Ecoandino Organic Purple Corn Kernel Powder
data.description: Ecoandino Organic Purple Corn Kernel Powder, distinguished by its light purple color, is a gluten-free, GMO-free, additive-free, and non-irradiated product. data.description: Ecoandino Organic Raw Camu Camu Whole Fruit Powder is a gluten-free, GMO-free, and additive-free product that maintains its purity and integrity.
